Package siminov.web.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdapterDescriptor
    Exposes methods to GET and SET Web Descriptor Adapter information as per define in WebDescriptor.si.xml file or standalone xml file in application.
    AdapterDescriptor.Handler
    Exposes methods to GET and SET Web Descriptor Adapter Handler information as per define in WebDescriptor.si.xml file or in standalone adapter xml file in application.
    AdapterDescriptor.Handler.Parameter
    Exposes methods to GET and SET Parameter information as per define in WebDescriptor.si.xml file or in standalone adapter xml file in application.
    AdapterDescriptor.Handler.Return
    Exposes methods to GET and SET Return information as per define in WebDescriptor.si.xml file or in standalone adapter xml file in application.
    ApplicationDescriptor
    Exposes methods to GET and SET Application Descriptor information as per define in ApplicationDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
    LibraryDescriptor
    Exposes methods to GET and SET Library Descriptor information as per define in LibraryDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
    WebSiminovDatas
    Exposes methods to GET and SET Siminov Web Datas structure.
    WebSiminovDatas.WebSiminovData
    Exposes methods to GET and SET Siminov Web Data structure.
    WebSiminovDatas.WebSiminovData.WebSiminovValue
    Exposes methods to GET and SET Siminov Web Value structure.
